title: Oke-Ode: Tragedy as Bandits Kill 15 Vigilantes, Hunters in Kwara
description: Bandits killed 15 vigilantes and hunters after invading the Oke-Ode community in Kwara State.

title: Bandits kill 12 forest guards in Kwara
description: Bandits attacked and killed 12 forest guards in the Oke-Ode area, with bodies found on the roadside.

title: Again, Bandits Wreak Havoc In Kwara
description: Bandits launched attacks in Kwara State, resulting in multiple deaths and kidnappings in the Oke-Ode community.
